title: The Foundation 01-05 (2008) cbr
description:
History shows that in the 1500s, Nostradamus' three volumes of prophecies were best-sellers, making him a rich man. But what the world does not know that he used his vast pool of resources to create a framework for the prevention of its most devastating prophecy from occurring! This secret team still functions today, using Nostradamus' published and unpublished volumes for forecasting security threats around the world.

enjoy
